trans-unit.source: Specifies the painting style applied to one <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" /> contained in a form.
trans-unit.target: 指定套用至表單中所包含之單一 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" /> 的繪製樣式。

trans-unit.source: You cannot explicitly set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to Custom.

However, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> returns Custom when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> is set to an extension of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer> class that is not <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>.
trans-unit.target: 不過，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>傳回自訂時<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>設定的延伸模組為<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer>不是類別<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer>或<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>。

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode" /> is not determined by the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager" /> or the use of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer" /> other than <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer" />
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode" /> 並非由 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager" /> 所決定，或者 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer" /> 而非 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer" /> 或 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer" /> 的用法。

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode" /> or <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer" /> determines the painting style.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode" /> 或 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer" /> 會決定繪製樣式。

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer" /> to paint.
trans-unit.target: 表示要繪製的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer" /> 之使用。

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer" /> to paint.
trans-unit.target: 表示要繪製的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer" /> 之使用。
